## EntityModelNodeOverride.remove() method

Removes this model node override from its parent entity.

**Signature:**

```typescript
remove(): void;
```
**Returns:**

void

## Remarks

This delegates to `Entity.removeModelNodeOverride()` so that map mutation and related event emission remain centralized on the entity.
